ould watch his Papa dive in the Olympics in person,\\\" Dustin penned on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9994846927449457, \"rank\": 0.00046114894185082605, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.949008057305232e-15, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our eldest son\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"his Papa dive\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"Dustin\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so proud of Tom for all of the sacrifices and incredibly hard work he's put in to get to his 5th Olympics and to make Robbie's wish come true!\\\"\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9994846927449457, \"rank\": 0.00046114894185082605, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"the sacrifices\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"his 5th Olympics\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a post-dive interview, Tom spoke of his decision to return to the competitive sport after floating the idea of retirement two years ago.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a post-dive interview\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitive sport\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1464}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"retirement\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think most of that [decision] was being able to set an example to my kids that if you have a dream and you work hard, it does not mean that you are always going to be able to achieve exactly what you want to, but it's about enjoying the process and doing what you can to show up, to be the best person that you can be.\\\"\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"decision\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1584}, {\"ngram\": \"my kids\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1766}, {\"ngram\": \"the best person\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The doting dad added: \\\"For me, this year is the happiest I have been in diving because diving wasn't necessarily my top priority.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The doting dad\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"my top priority\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, it was extremely important.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is nothing more important than my children and being able to spend time with them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"my children\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2095}]}]}"